mbox{par}}+{\mbox{5}})}"></span>. If there are at least 5 but fewer than 20=
 qualifying scores available, the handicap index is calculated using a set =
number or differentials according to how many scores are available, with an=
 additional adjustment made to that average in some circumstances.
</p>
