<p>The basic formula for calculating the handicap index is as follows (wher=
e <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"m=
we-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math =
