-align: -1.838ex; width:76.884ex; height:5.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {\=
mbox{Playing handicap}}=3D{\frac {({\mbox{handicap index}}\times {\mbox{slo=
pe rating}})}{\mbox{113}}}+({\mbox{course rating}}-{\mbox{par}})}"></span><=
/dd></dl>
<p>And for category 6 a "playing handicap differential" is used, which is e=
qual to the playing handicap for a handicap index of 36.0:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
