{\mbox{113}}{\mbox{Slope Rating}}}}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>To calculate the GA handicap, the "sloped played to" results are average=
d and multiplied by a factor of 0.93, which is intended to equalize the han=
dicap in favor of better players. The formula for calculating a GA handicap=
 is as follows (where <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inli=
ne"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"di=
splay: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D=
"{\displaystyle n}">
